job.title: School Education Dept Punjab Lecturer Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 569 Vacancy
job.body:
Total Vacancies:569

Name of the post:

  • Lecturer (Biology, Chemistry, Commerce, Economics, Geography, Hindi, Maths, Sociology)

Description:

School Education Dept Punjab issued a total of 569 vacancies for the posts of Lecturer. The online application for these posts under SEDP shall start from 05-04-2021 The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 05-05-2021 For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com.The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for School Education Dept Punjab Lecturer Recruitment 2021:

  • Mode of application: Online
  • The application fee for theGEN & Other Category is 1000/-
  • The application fee for sc/ ST the category is 500/-

For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 05-04-2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 26-04-2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the Degree in M.Sc, B.Ed, B.Com/ CA/ ICWA, B.Ed to apply for the post of Lecturer

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is:18 years
  • The maximum age required to apply is: 32 years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Lecturer is: 16,000-39,000 per month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that SEDP issued this notification for which posts.

How to apply for School Education Dept Punjab Lecturer Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of SEDP
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Lecturer
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
